snippet.title: WATCH LIVE | Election results as Biden overtakes Trump in Georgia and Pennsylvania
snippet.description:
Joe Biden overtook President Trump in the count in Pennsylvania on the morning of Nov. 6. The count is ongoing, but Pennsylvania’s 20 electoral votes would put Biden over the 270 votes needed even with a handful of other states still too close to call.

Biden also took a small lead in Georgia, though vote counting is not yet complete. Thousands of requested overseas and military ballots may arrive by the deadline and there are provisional ballots left to count. Read more: https://wapo.st/36adqBN.
